column1: There are many kinds of travellers - there are the ones who travel with nothing but the twinkle in their eye and a map in their pocket. Although it sounds like it would be great fun to be like that
column2: you are not. You are the polar opposite who makes a list and has thought everything through. Making lists and preparing itineraries
column3:
you along with your American Tourister 15 Inch Laptop Backpack are unstoppable.

Body

column1: When you decide to go someplace
column2: there is nothing that escapes your iron-clad research. You go through notes of history
column4: socio-political scene
column5: cuisine and lifestyle. Your analytical mind draws a detailed sketch of where all you would go with your unisex backpack. You even carry a soft copy of this program in your laptop within this 15 inch backpack which measures 320 x 410 x 170 mm in dimension. You follow the schedule to the last dot but the last day is always kept free for any unexpected surprise or plan. This backpack is made of dobby nylon and twill fabric

column1: The plane descends on time and you are out of the airport with this backpack right on time. No time to spare
column2: after a quick coffee and croissant it is time to head out. The itinerary begins with a panoramic tour of the best sights of the city. There is so much to see and you have worn your walking shoes to make sure nothing stands in the way. This backpack is ideal for this panoramic walk as it comes with back padding that is comfortable and keeps away strain. You can keep your journal
column3: towel and travel guides in the 2 compartments and  side pockets. Even an unexpected rain shower does not interfere with your thoroughly made plans. You simply take out your umbrella and put the rain cover on this backpack.

column1: The earphone access allows you to listen to music
column2: making those long walks and long queues enjoyable. The zip pocket for coins is very useful as you don’t have to go through the entire backpack if you pass by a vending machine. To keep your items safe in case you get mugged
column3: this backpack also comes with a secret pocket to keep essential documents and money. Apart from all this
column4: it also comes with a multi-utility pouch and key holder. This American Tourister backpack takes care of all your worries so that you can enjoy the journey.
